足都有責任打好呢場資訊戰，改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube戰線：黃色資訊片一律Coment+Like+Share&amp;Subscribe（CLS)（share做唔到的話重要片先share)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=70490c8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},{"pid":"c1198623b7886cab25930898b0e370d6e12d6818","tid":1889652,"uid":32665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"市民回應警員聚餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1889696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1889696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"59697067fda70b93ae99555fdd5bd13a4ae1f20f","tid":1889652,"uid":109690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:43:10.000Z","msg":"手足們小心啲唔好俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7954b20557f0809ec97cda9e5f6a388a320c27","tid":1889652,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:48:52.000Z","msg":"唔好指意出解放軍<br />\n老解自己一早都中撚晒招啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e0e5fb0927457d1c66df64258923a119f4f443","tid":1889652,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T18:51:49.000Z","msg":"辛亥革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccd4465ab6c1e423e333306c028476bc3169aea","tid":1889652,"uid":105773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:58:30.000Z","msg":"公安大條道理入來執法"}]}